  <data key="d4">Famous for its wildlife, especially for tigers and elephants, Rajaji National Park is a Tiger Reserve. It is spread over 3 districts of Uttarakhand including Dehradun, Haridwar and Pauri Garhwal. Apart from the Jeep Safari and Elephant Safari, the 34 km jungle track is a major attraction here.</data>
